```plantuml
@startuml Simon-0711_ta_lyrics_sentiment_classification

actor User
participant Frontend as "Frontend (React)"
participant Backend as "Backend (FastAPI)"
participant Elasticsearch
participant LyricsGeniusAPI as "LyricsGenius API"
participant CNNModel as "CNN Model"

User -> Frontend: Input song/artist info
Frontend -> Backend: POST /search (song details)
alt Lyrics in Elasticsearch?
    Backend -> Elasticsearch: Query lyrics by song/artist
    Elasticsearch --> Backend: Return lyrics data
else Lyrics not found
    Backend -> LyricsGeniusAPI: Fetch lyrics
    LyricsGeniusAPI --> Backend: Return raw lyrics
    Backend -> Backend: Preprocess lyrics\n(normalize, tokenize)
    Backend -> CNNModel: Classify sentiment
    CNNModel --> Backend: Return mood classification
    Backend -> Elasticsearch: Store new lyrics\nwith classification
end

Backend -> Elasticsearch: Query similar songs\nby mood/features
Elasticsearch --> Backend: Return similar songs
Backend -> Backend: Calculate cosine similarity\n(TF-IDF)
Backend --> Frontend: Return classification\n+ recommendations
Frontend --> User: Display results

@enduml
```